item.title: Packaging problem of my keyauth project that I wrote with C# winform?
item.dc:creator: mak
item.description:
You need to set VMP settings to ignore the JSON attributes used in KeyAuth.cs, such as success, message, etc. These cannot be renamed by an obfuscator renamer or it breaks the program.

The default VMP settings work fine for me, so it’s a configuration problem with your VMP instance. Just play around with it and you should get it working.

Read full topic
